title: Daily Wire Backstage: Super Tuesday 2020 Edition
description:
Will Democrats ensure Bernie’s star burns up? Will Liz quit yet ANOTHER race she didn’t belong in? Does Joe Biden know where he is right now?!

Join this roundtable discussion featuring Ben Shapiro, Andrew Klavan, Michael Knowles, and Daily Wire god-king Jeremy Boreing as they get to the bottom of these questions and more.
